<br>
With 35-36 Enh buffs, my Weaponskill is around 1750.  When I group with the odd 40+ Enh cleric, my Weaponskill is bumped just over 1800.<br>
<br>
That 50 difference in Weaponskill has a large impact.  With it, I've managed to solo 2 SB's at once, then badly hurt a 3rd that joined the fight right at the end.<br>
<br>
There is a difference IMO.  Enough that I get giddy when I group with a 40 Enh cleric. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=vasagh>Vasagh</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 42<br> <font color=#000000>(6/3/03 1:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22.topic&index=27>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Weaponskill</span><hr size=1> Interesting I'll have to try it out if I can find a cleric with high enhance. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm19.showMessageRange?topicID=22.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm19.showPrevMessage?topicID=22.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm19.showNextMessage?topicID=22.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=22.topic&index=27><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm19.emailToFriend?topicID=22.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm19.threadControl?topicID=22.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdao